{
    "name": "升级",
    "icon": "productivebees:upgrade_base",
    "category": "productivebees:items",
    "pages": [
        {
            "type": "patchouli:spotlight",
            "item": "productivebees:upgrade_base",
            "text": "可以对机器和蜂巢进行升级，以增加其功能或提高其性能"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/base",
            "text": "其他所有升级的基础"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/breeding",
            "text": "可用于：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩容后的蜂箱$(/l)，$(l:blocks/catcher)捕捉器$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "babee"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "安装在蜂箱中时，升级：繁殖允许蜜蜂在无人参与的情况下小概率繁殖并产生新的后代。请注意，不能正常繁殖的蜜蜂无法使用此升级。$(br)当安装在$(l:blocks/catcher)捕捉器$(/l)中时，只有小蜜蜂会被捕捉并放入笼子中。"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/productivity",
            "text": "可用于：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩容后的蜂箱$(/l)，$(l:blocks/honey_generator)蜂蜜发电机$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "productivity"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "安装在蜂箱中时，升级：产量会增加蜜蜂每次生产的蜜脾数量。可以安装多个升级：产量。"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/time",
            "text": "可用于：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩容后的蜂箱$(/l)，$(l:blocks/centrifuge)离心机$(/l)，$(l:blocks/incubator)小蜜蜂孵化器$(/l)，$(l:blocks/honey_generator)蜂蜜发电机(/l)。",
            "anchor": "speed"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "当安装在蜂箱中时，速度升级将减少蜜蜂在蜂箱中停留的时间。(br)当安装在$(l:blocks/centrifuge)离心机$(/l)或、$(l:blocks/incubator)小蜜蜂孵化器$(/l)中时，它将提高运行速度。"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/filter",
            "text": "可用于：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩容后的蜂箱$(/l)，$(l:blocks/catcher)捕捉器$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "filter"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "Right click on a bee to add it to the filter. Put the filter in a crafting grid to clear it. When installed in a hive, only bees specified on the filter will be allowed to enter. $(br)When installed in a catcher, only the bees specified on the filter will be picked up."
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/range",
            "text": "可用于：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩容后的蜂箱$(/l)，$(l:blocks/catcher)捕捉器$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "range"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "安装在蜂箱中时，农夫蜜蜂和收集/囤积者蜜蜂的工作半径每次升级都会增加1，无升级为4。当安装在捕捉器中时，范围升级将在所有方向上扩大1个方块的工作范围。可安装多个范围升级。"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/anti_teleport",
            "text": "可用于：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩容后的蜂箱$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "anti_teleport"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "安装在蜂箱中时，可以传送的蜜蜂生活时将不再传送。"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/bee_sampler",
            "text": "可用于：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩容后的蜂箱$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "sampler"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "安装在蜂箱中时，每次蜜蜂回巢都会提取少量基因。这不会对蜜蜂造成任何伤害。可在同一蜂箱中安装多个，以提高效率。"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/comb_block",
            "text": "可用于：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩容后的蜂箱$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "comb_block"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "安装在蜂箱中时，蜜蜂会产生完整的蜜脾块，而不是蜜脾。"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:crafting",
            "recipe": "productivebees:upgrades/simulator",
            "text": "可用于：$(l:hives/advanced_hives#expanded)扩容后的蜂箱$(/l)。",
            "anchor": "simulator"
        },
        {
            "type": "patchouli:text",
            "text": "安装在蜂箱中时，蜜蜂将不再从蜂箱中出来，而是模拟它们的采花行程，以提高服务器性能。采蜜方块或装有花朵的饲养板必须放在蜂箱脚下，不能挡住前面，而要在其正下方。"
        },
